item.title: Privilege: Tidbits to Tidle Waves and Final Outcomes
item.description: What is privilege? Did I really have an advantage as a white male in America? It isn’t as bad as other places right? So I shouldn’t worry about it I guess. Link to the comic itself. The Pencilsword: On a plate.
